Convention sharing with skill-tuning
--------------------------------------

When `skill-dev-toolkit:skill-tuning` ships (PR-3 of this series), the
following 3 convention files will be present as functional copies
in both skills' `references/`:

- `golden-anchor-protocol.md`
- `test-prompts-schema.md`
- `constitution-schema.md`

**Same-PR drift rule**: any edit to
the protocol must update both copies in the same PR. This skill
ships the canonical content for these conventions in PR-2;
`skill-tuning` will copy them verbatim plus a header blockquote
pointing back. Drift between the two copies is a regression
caught by future cross-skill CI (PR-4 of this series).
